description_0: A white 1985 CJ7 Jeep parked by a curbside of a neighborhood. The car has large tires, 1 large and small circle lights by the sides of the grill, the bumper is a straight metal piece with a license plate to the left side, the car has beige designs on the hood and by the front curve of the hood in bold is the text "LAREDO." To the left is a lawn of grass by a metal fence, a tree and a home with an abstract wall with a white door. To the right is a white SUV reversing out of a drive way, There are many trees in the background under a white sky. daytime.
description_1: A close up view of the front exterior of a red 1966 Dodge D series pickup truck parked in a parking lot flanked by 2 sedans on either side. The left sedan is blue and the right sedan is gray."DODGE" is written in dull silver letters across the front of the hood. The "G" in "DODGE" is smudged with something black. The bumper of the truck is white. The paint on the truck is slightly faded. A parking lot filled with vehicles is visible behind the truck. To the right of the truck, there is a tree, a small red table with benches, and a black metal pole.
